data-triple-N3.o: "Chrysler Group LLC is an American automobile manufacturer headquartered in Auburn Hills, Michigan. Principally owned by majority shareholder Fiat, Chrysler is one of the "Big Three" American automobile manufacturers. It sells vehicles worldwide under its flagship Chrysler brand, as well as the Dodge, Jeep, and Ram brands; it also manufactures vehicles sold under the Fiat brand in North America."@en
